# Roborock Cleaning Schedule
# Supercronic logs all output to stdout/stderr automatically
# Times run in the TZ configured in .env
#
# The Roborock app only supports simple schedules - specialized cleaning
# tasks live here, composed directly from roborock.py commands.
#
# Examples (uncomment / edit to build the schedule):
#
# Weekday morning high-traffic clean: kitchen + hallway, 2 passes, no mop
# 0 10 * * 1-5 roborock.py clean --rooms Kitchen Hallway --passes 2 --fan balanced --water off
#
# Weekly deep clean: whole home, max suction, mopping
# 0 10 * * 6 roborock.py clean --passes 1 --fan max --water medium
